want privacy now?

755
00:36:15.073 --> 00:36:16.198
I'll be upstairs.

756
00:36:20.203 --> 00:36:21.287
Rocky...

757
00:36:22.664 --> 00:36:24.832
Rocky, I'm sorry.
I... I...

758
00:36:24.916 --> 00:36:28.377
But, you know, it just takes one
bad hit, and you could be an invalid.

759
00:36:28.462 --> 00:36:30.337
Well, I feel like
an invalid already, Adrian.

760
00:36:30.422 --> 00:36:31.589
