764
00:36:37.012 --> 00:36:39.597
She said, you know, she
could use some part-time help.

765
00:36:39.681 --> 00:36:41.182
Yeah, but why do you
wanna do this, Adrian?

766
00:36:41.266 --> 00:36:43.392
Why do you wanna go back to
the same place you started from?

767
00:36:43.477 --> 00:36:45.478
I gotta do it,
but you don't gotta do it!

768
00:36:45.562 --> 00:36:49.023
I wanted to be there so
I could be close to you.

769
00:36:58.408 --> 00:36:59.950
All right. Yeah.

770
00:37:00.035 --> 00:37:02.203
You know, it's getting a
little cold out here. Maybe...

771
00:37:02.287 --> 00:37:03.996
Okay. Maybe you
better get inside, okay?

772
00:37:04.080 --> 00:37:05.122
I understand.

773
00:37:05.207 --> 00:37:06.999
Are you all right?
What?

774
00:37:07.083 --> 00:37:08.083
Are you all right?

775
00:37:08.168 --> 00:37:09.794
Yeah, I'm all right.
I'm fine.

776
00:37:09.878 --> 00:37:11.629
Hey, it's getting cold, okay?

777
00:37:17.886 --> 00:37:21.680
Yo, Adrian!
Did we ever leave this place?

778
00:37:24.476 --> 00:37:26.227
