790
00:38:10.438 --> 00:38:11.438
All right?

791
00:38:14.067 --> 00:38:16.110
None of these bums
think straight.

792
00:38:20.782 --> 00:38:22.283
All I need is a hook.

793
00:38:34.129 --> 00:38:36.255
Hey, ain't you Rocky's kid?

