cojones knocked out.

842
00:40:24.364 --> 00:40:26.156
Okay. Ready, guy?

843
00:40:26.241 --> 00:40:28.534
Benson, go easy, all right?

844
00:40:28.618 --> 00:40:30.536
Sure. Okay, Rock.
Time.

