886
00:41:49.991 --> 00:41:51.366
How about you
try to manage me?

887
00:41:51.451 --> 00:41:52.451
Manage?

888
00:41:52.535 --> 00:41:56.163
Yeah, unless you think
I ain't got nothing going.

889
00:41:56.247 --> 00:41:57.873
Man, got nothing going?

890
00:41:57.957 --> 00:42:00.542
Yeah, all right, you got a lot
going. You got a lot of tools.

891
00:42:00.627 --> 00:42:03.253
But I ain't no manager.
I ain't never been...

892
00:42:03.338 --> 00:42:05.255
You know,
the gentleman that owned this place,

893
00:42:05.340 --> 00:42:06.423
that was a manager.

894
00:42:06.508 --> 00:42:10.511
