who just come up on the roof.

1363
01:05:52.098 --> 01:05:55.142
You know, hey, you know, he
just landed there and crashed.

1364
01:05:55.227 --> 01:05:56.352
And who do you
think it is?

1365
01:05:56.436 --> 01:05:58.395
Do I hear
reindeer on my roof?

1366
01:05:59.356 --> 01:06:01.023
You know...

1367
01:06:01.107 --> 01:06:02.107
Rantlers.

1368
01:06:02.192 --> 01:06:04.610
Unbelievable.
It's like a billion...

