01:06:11.243 --> 01:06:13.202
It's gonna be next Christmas
before he gets down.

1374
01:06:13.286 --> 01:06:16.580
Hey, let's put it together for Santa! Hey!

1375
01:06:16.665 --> 01:06:18.332
Merry X-mas. Yo, yo, yo.

1376
01:06:18.416 --> 01:06:20.501
Hey, I don't think
you got it right, Santa.

1377
01:06:20.585 --> 01:06:23.629
No, no, no.
It's, "Ho, ho, ho."

1378
01:06:23.713 --> 01:06:24.755
What's
the freaking difference?

1379
01:06:24.839 --> 01:06:26.590
Where I come from,
it's, "Yo, yo, yo."

1380
01:06:26.675 --> 01:06:29.051
Looks like we got
a 90-proof Santa.

1381
01:06:29.135 --> 01:06:30.928
Hey, Santa,

1382
01:06:31.012 --> 01:06:33.722
tell all the kids what
you got in the bag for them

1383
01:06:33.807 --> 01:06:35.224
that you brought
from the North.

1384
01:06:35.308 --> 01:06:37.059
Yeah, I got my laundry.

1385
01:06:37.143 --> 01:06:38.727
No, you got the wrong bag.

1386
01:06:38.812 --> 01:06:40.813
Come on, chubby, get out
of the way. Yo, watch it.

1387
01:06:40.897 --> 01:06:42.064
