01:06:42.482 --> 01:06:43.941
Come here, little boy.
You been nice?

1389
01:06:44.067 --> 01:06:46.068
Uncle Paulie! Come over here. Sit down here.

1390
01:06:46.152 --> 01:06:48.654
Hey, kid, why don't you tell
Santa what you need? What you...

