you ain't the same either.

1426
01:08:08.735 --> 01:08:09.777
What?

1427
01:08:13.740 --> 01:08:15.741
Adrian, what...
What did I do?

1428
01:08:16.451 --> 01:08:17.576
Go talk to him.

1429
01:08:21.414 --> 01:08:23.832
