nobody, so I got no time for you.

1444
01:08:59.536 --> 01:09:00.869
Hey, what are you
saying to me, kid?

1445
01:09:00.954 --> 01:09:02.246
You're like another person.

1446
01:09:02.330 --> 01:09:04.206
