watch out for scams and deceptions?

1454
01:09:19.305 --> 01:09:20.389
Yeah?

1455
01:09:20.932 --> 01:09:23.809
You're the one that should have watched out.

1456
01:09:30.900 --> 01:09:32.568
Where you going?
Out.

1457
01:09:32.652 --> 01:09:34.445
